\c 23
\s Jobho anoshuva kurondedzera nyaya yake pamberi paMwari
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jobho wakapindura ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Kunyange nhasi\x + Zek. 9.12.\x* gunun'uno yangu inorwadza\x + 21.4.\x*; ruoko rwangu rwunorema pamusoro pekugomera kwangu.
\v 3 Haiwa, dai ndaiziva kwandingamuwana\x + 13.3. 16.21.\x*. Ndaiuya panzvimbo yake\x + Eze. 43.11. Nah. 2.9.\x*.
\v 4 Ndairongedza nyaya \add yangu\add* pamberi pake\x + 13.18.\x*, ndokuzadza muromo wangu nenharo\x + 13.6.\x*.
\v 5 Ndinoziva mashoko \add a\add*anondipindura, uye ndinonzwisisa zvaachareva kwandiri.
\v 6 Achandipikisa neukuru hwesimba here? Kwete, asi iye achaisa \add moyo wake\add* kwandiri\x + 30.18. 9.34. 13.21.\x*.
\v 7 Ipapo wakarurama angapikisana naye; naizvozvo ndainunurwa rinhi narinhi pamutongi wangu.
\v 8 Tarira\x + 9.11.\x*, ndinoenda mberi, asi haapo\x + 18.20.\x*; uye shure\x + 18.20.\x*, asi handimunzwisisi\x + 9.11.\x*.
\v 9 Kuruboshwe pakushanda kwake, asi handimutariri\x + Gen.. 14.15.\x*; anozvivanza parudyi\x + 1 Sam. 23.19.\x*, uye handimuoni\x + 9.11.\x*.
\v 10 Asi anoziva nzira neni\x + Map. 139.1-3.\x*; ngaandiidze; ndichabuda segoridhe\x + Map. 17.3. 66.10. Jak. 1.12.\x*.
\v 11 Rutsoka rwangu rwakabatirira paakatsika\x + Map. 44.18.\x*; ndakachengeta nzira yake, uye handina kutsauka\x + Map. 125.5.\x*.
\v 12 Handina kubva pamurairo wemiromo yake; ndakakoshesa mashoko emuromo wake kupfuura mugove wangu.
\v 13 Asi iye ari pane chimwe, uye ndiani anomudzosera shure\x + 9.12.\x*? Uye anoita zvinoda mweya wake\x + Map. 115.3.\x*.
\v 14 Nokuti anopedza zvandakatemerwa; nezvizhinji zvakadai zviri kwaari\x + 10.13.\x*.
\v 15 Naizvozvo ndinovhunduka pamberi pake; ndinofunga, ndinomutya\x + Marir. 4.16.\x*.
\v 16 Nokuti Mwari anoita moyo wangu upere simba, uye Wemasimbaose wakandivhundusa\x + Det. 20.3. Map. 22.14.\x*.
\v 17 Nokuti handina kugurwa pamberi perima\x + 17.12. 22.11.\x*, uye wakafukidza rima\x + 10.22.\x* pachiso changu\x + 9.27.\x*.